{"tid":201290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教會人士耶穌受難日出動，到天后廟外重演耶穌被釘十字架","createTime":"2017-04-14T15:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T14:47:52.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2fce28884a93bb3b3020be8328a08b90e07923","tid":201290,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"教會人士耶穌受難日出動，到天后廟外重演耶穌被釘十字架<br />\n作者：熱血編輯部 (陳五)  14/4/2017<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201704/17903928_1281658338556058_6318927066434666079_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201704%2F17903928_1281658338556058_6318927066434666079_n.jpg&h=8ec80240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源：陳到 Do Chan 專頁）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日（4月14日）為耶穌受難日，不少宗教團體都舉辦活動，去紀念捨己救人的主耶穌。不過就有人發現，又有人在令人莫名其妙的地方，舉辦耶穌受難日的活動。<br />\n<br />\n消息指在今日晚上，有一班教會人士，去到油麻地眾坊街的天后古廟外，掛起了「耶穌是主」及「耶穌在廟街」的橫額，並有一名扮演耶穌的男子，在廟外重演被釘十字架一幕，恐怕又會引起另一波的爭議。 <br />\n<br />\n翻查宗教刊物《奇妙恩典》，相關活動已非首次舉行。 <br />\n<br />\n在2015年的平安夜，在相同的位置上，有教會人士在廟外掛上「聖誕報佳音」的橫額，被網民批評為不懂尊重其他宗教。<br />\n<br />\n轉載自熱血時報網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/04-14-2017/37255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F04-14-2017%2F37255&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=cbf1309f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/04-14-2017/37255</a>"},{"pid":"dbe9196bf15e0a73b9eaea721c00a8b1fe3154cf","tid":201290,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"耶撚真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e092cc0e08689d6d082321c59c5779dec948f5","tid":201290,"uid":76681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"wa.....出血呀佢...<br />\n<br 